---
title: Nan's Pork Rissoles & Cheesy Fries with Apple Salad & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Nan’s special seasoning is full of flavour, thanks to paprika, pepper, onion and garlic, and when used to make these rissoles, it's
simply heavenly! Add a crisp apple salad and cheesy fries and it’s satisfaction, guaranteed.
